- **Leapfrog**: 500 geometric steps, KDK with Hubble drag (`Δv = F·dt − v·(da/a)`)
- **GPU**: NVIDIA RTX PRO 6000 Blackwell (95 GiB VRAM), Warp CIC + torch cuFFT
